title: Sample Book (USA), ca. 1920
description: Sample book of woolen suiting fabric from various manufacturers in plain colors, plaids and various weaves.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book (USA), ca. 1920; Manufactured by Richard Fensterer and Company (United States); clothbound covers, woven wool samples; H x W: 46 x 52 cm (18 1/8 x 20 1/2 in.); 1960-69-1
